text: Kennan Gilchrist (born September 13, 1994) is a professional Canadian football linebacker for the Toronto Argonauts of the Canadian Football League (CFL). He began his professional career as an undrafted free agent signing with the Dallas Cowboys on April 30, 2017. He was released following training camp and then spent time with the Houston Texans and San Antonio Commanders. Following the suspension and bankruptcy of the Alliance of American Football, Gilchrist signed with the Argonauts on April 16, 2019.
